  79,38,Ka gahim Dunia bi…õhigu
  79,39,T…Ē! Achiika! ∆∑ehiimi bu…£um n-ny…õ o labbu shee
  79,40,"Amaa! Ninvu…£u so Ňčun zo o Duuma (Naawuni) tooni zanibu, ka m…ĒŇč o maŇč‚Äô suhuyurlim"
  79,41,T…Ē! Achiika! Alizanda n-ny…õ o labbu shee
  79,42,"(Yaa nyini Annabi)! B…õ b…Ēhira n-zaŇč chaŇč saha (Chiyaama yi…£isibu), ni bondali ka di y…õn ti niŇč"
  79,43,Yapolo ka a y…õn ny…õ di baŇčsim y…õli ba
